OL,3,CFather jailed for violence and racist
OL,4,Cremarks hung head in shame in court
OL,6,FA father-of-four has been jailed for
OL,7,F28 months after throwing a missile and
OL,8,Fshouting racist remarks during a
OL,9,Fprotest in Tamworth.
OL,11,FDavid Jordan, 59, was charged with
OL,12,Fviolent disorder after video footage
OL,13,Fshowed him throwing an object towards
OL,14,Fa line of police in front of the
OL,15,FHoliday Inn Express hotel in the
OL,16,FStaffordshire town, where migrants
OL,17,Fwere being housed, on August 4.
