OL,6,FJordan, who was identified anonymously
OL,7,Fby a member of the public, was seen on
OL,8,Fmultiple videos goading police
OL,9,Fofficers, making inappropriate
OL,10,Fgestures, throwing missiles from
OL,11,Fbehind a road-sign and enticing the
OL,12,Fcrowd.
OL,14,FThe defendant, of Tamworth Road,
OL,15,FTamworth, could also be heard shouting
OL,16,F"f****** paedos" towards the hotel and
OL,17,Ftelling police officers to "f*** off".
