OL,6,FHe also messaged a contact on Facebook
OL,7,Fasking them to spread the word that
OL,8,Fsome migrants had been moved to a
OL,9,Fdifferent hotel.
OL,11,FProsecution barrister Fiona Cortese
OL,12,Ftold the court that during a police
OL,13,Finterview, Jordan said he had not
OL,14,Fplanned to attend the protest and that
OL,15,Fhe was an "angry old man shouting his
OL,16,Fmouth off".
