OL,4,Cremarks hung head in shame in court
OL,6,FDefending Jordan, Harinderpal Singh
OL,7,FDhami said: "As far as the harm is
OL,8,Fconcerned, I imagine the fear the
OL,9,Fpeople in the hotel felt, the police,
OL,10,Fand the community as a whole watching
OL,11,Fon the TV.
OL,13,F"He now accepts fully the way he
OL,14,Fconducted himself was far from a
OL,15,Fpeaceful protest."
OL,17,FSentencing him at Stafford Crown
OL,18,FCourt, Judge John Edwards told Jordan:
OL,19,F"You rightly hung your head in shame
OL,20,Fas we watched the video.
