OL,6,F"I have looked with care at the
OL,7,Ffootage, you are front and centre of
OL,8,Fthis baying mob for an hour-and-a-
OL,9,Fhalf."
OL,11,FAssistant Chief Constable Stuart
OL,12,FEllison said: "This is the first
OL,13,Fconviction we've secured in
OL,14,FStaffordshire and it certainly won't
OL,15,Fbe the last.
OL,17,F"Our officers have been working
OL,18,Fincredibly long hours to investigate
OL,19,Fthe vast array of footage available
OL,20,Ffrom both incidents we've experienced
OL,21,Facross Stoke-on-Trent and Tamworth.
