OL,6,F"I want to be clear that robust
OL,7,Fenforcement is continuing each and
OL,8,Fevery day across the country and in
OL,9,FStaffordshire. We've arrested 51
OL,10,Fpeople and charged 17 with violent
OL,11,Fdisorder offences so far, and more
OL,12,Fwill be coming.
OL,14,F"I'd also like to recognise the vital
OL,15,Frole that the public have played in
OL,16,Fthis conviction, too. We're continuing
OL,17,Fto receive information from members of
OL,18,Fthe local community through our major
OL,19,Fincident portal, which is an integral
OL,20,Fpart of securing the evidence needed
OL,21,Fto deliver justice.
